  "title": "Project Site Engineer (Construction)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To perform engineer’s role on method statement, implement cost &amp; time efficiency on operation</li>\n  <li>To checking plans, drawings and quantities for accuracy of calculations</li>\n  <li>To supervise site works compliances and inspection requirement</li>\n  <li>To carry out daily site supervision, coordination and quality assurance of all trades implementation on site</li>\n  <li>To work closely with sub-contractors on project progress and ensure timely work arrangements</li>\n  <li>To scheduling materials and equipment purchases and deliveries</li>\n  <li>To liaise with consultant and carry out site inspection</li>\n  <li>Attend all site's meeting on work progression</li>\n  <li>To prepare monthly meeting progression report</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess Degree in Civil Engineering</li>\n  <li>3 years working experience in Construction</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently</li>\n  <li>Have positive attitude</li>\n</ul>",
